quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"MoЖґЖґere alaa e ko heewi e ndeeyuuji maЙ“Й“e Й—i, si wonaa oon jamirЙ—o sadaka, maa moЖґЖґere maa moЖґЖґiЕ‹tingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala baЙ—irЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol weluya Alla, arma min ngokka mo njoЙ“di mawndi."
  4,115,"Kala luutndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde paawal ngal Й“anngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gooЕЉЙ—inЙ“e Й“en, Men kuccintinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, min naatnЙ—um Jahannama, nge bonii ruttorde !"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yafatako waЙ—deedel mo e goЙ—Й—um, Homo yaafo ko jaasi Й—um wonan de on mo o muuyi. Kala denndinЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gooЕ‹Й—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—oynde."
  4,117,"ЖЃe ndewaani ko woori Alla, si wonaa [sanamuuji] dewЙ—inaaЙ—i, Й“e ndwaani si wanaa seytaane canndalinЙ—o."
  4,118,"Alla HuЙ—ii mbo: owi"mami jogito e jeyaaЙ“e maa Й“en geЙ—al ganndangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinЙ“e, ma mi yelinoyЙ“e, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e taЖґ noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e mbaylu tagoore Alla nde !". Kala jogitiiЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o ko woori Alla, gooЕ‹Й—ii o perti perte Й“anngunde."
  4,120,"Hombo Й“ef odana homo yelina Й“e, seytaane fodanani Й“e si wanaa hodo.(koomte)."
  4,121,"ЖЃeen Й—on jaaЖґndee maЙ“Й“e nde ko Jahannama, Й“e keЙ“ataa gaa nge daЙ—irde."